    <introduction>
      <Value><![CDATA[<p>These regulations take effect from October 2014 and supersede all previous regulations.</p>
<p>These regulations should be read in conjunction with the University’s Extenuating Circumstances Policy.</p>
<p>Under these regulations, a University officer may act through his or her properly appointed nominee.</p>]]></Value>
